name: Feed your cat.
description:
Premise:

You wake up in the middle of the night as your cat is in desperate need of food. The game has six endings in total.

Inspirations:

GASA4

Forget Your Friend's Birthday

Doghouse 2

Notes:

This is my very first game and it might be kinda buggy. If you find any bugs please report them. I might update it in the future and add more endings or maybe I'll make a sequel.
